📌 Project Overview

This project focuses on analyzing crowdfunding data using SQL.
It includes data cleaning, transformation, and generating insights to understand successful projects.

⸻

🛠️ Tools & Technologies
	•	MySQL
	•	SQL (Joins, Aggregations, CTEs)
	•	Data Cleaning & Transformation

⸻

📂 Dataset Description

The dataset contains crowdfunding project details such as:
	•	Project Name
	•	Funding Goal
	•	Amount Raised (USD)
	•	Number of Backers
	•	Project Status
	•	Timestamps (created, launched, deadline, etc.)

⸻

⚙️ Data Cleaning & Transformation
	•	Converted epoch timestamps into readable datetime format
	•	Created new date columns for analysis
	•	Handled null and missing values
	•	Structured dataset for better querying

⸻

📅 Calendar Table Creation
	•	Built a dynamic calendar table using recursive CTE
	•	Extracted:
	•	Year, Month, Quarter
	•	Weekday details
	•	Financial month & quarter

⸻

📊 Key Analysis Performed

🔝 Top Successful Projects (By Backers)
	•	Identified projects with highest number of supporters

💰 Top Successful Projects (By Amount Raised)
	•	Found projects with highest funding

